Package pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model

Interface IMatrix<T>

Type Parameters:
T - generic type that can be stored inside matrix
All Known Implementing Classes:
Matrix
public interface IMatrix<T>
An inteface in the 'model' package. It represents the matrix in any way possible. The interface defines methods needed for classes implementing the matrix concept.

1.2
